query:
SELECT id, name, slug, regularPrice, salePrice, categoryId 
FROM products 
WHERE name LIKE '%Blessing%' OR name LIKE '%Lamp%' OR name LIKE '%Incense%' OR name LIKE '%祈福%'
ORDER BY id;
